description:
Check out this video for a sneak peek at the brand-new AYANEO Pocket DS! It’s a dual-screen handheld gaming device with a massive 7-inch AMOLED screen and a smaller 5-inch 4.3-inch screen. It’s perfect for playing retro games and emulating consoles like the Wii U, 3DS, Nintendo DS, and more!

Powered by the Snapdragon G3X Gen 2 and up to 16GB of RAM, this handheld is turning out to be quite impressive!
